{"tid":472041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"感動中華！！中國製造品質世界第一！！！！","createTime":"2017-11-17T23:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T06:53:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf7043e46e7b9b772de2832c355b48f67e89d7b","tid":472041,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/073417_c3c12698de09883af5a18218bfa5867a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F073417_c3c12698de09883af5a18218bfa5867a.jpg&h=ef031e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n產品製造國調查：德國居首 日本第8 中國墊底<br />\n<br />\n2017/10/26 18:04<br />\n鉅亨網新聞中心<br />\n消費者對產地有印象分數（圖:AFP）<br />\n消費者對產地有印象分數（圖:AFP）<br />\n新買一樣東西，你希望看到標籤上註明是在那裡製造？每個人心中對不同國家產品，都有個既定印象，其實也關係著你願意出價多少錢買進。<br />\n<br />\n根據市場調查機構 Statista 公布的國家製造指數 (Made-In-Country-Index, MICI)，結果顯示，「德國製造」是全球最受尊敬，其次是瑞士及歐盟，「台灣製造」排名中、後段班，落後南韓、波蘭及俄羅斯，中國、孟加拉及越南在這份指數中墊底。<br />\n<br />\n國家製造指數（圖表取自Business Insider）<br />\n國家製造指數（圖表取自 Business Insider）<br />\n這份調查共收集全球 52 個國家或地區，合計 43034 人的意見，每位受訪者可以列出自己認為產品最優質的產地，共有 129102 個數據，並依此排名，主要測量的是「印象分數」。<br />\n<br />\n依調查結果，共 49 個國家及地區列入排名, 消費者對歐盟產品印象普遍較佳，前 5 名都是歐洲國家，包括第 4 名的英國、第 5 名的瑞典，而第 7 名義大利及第 9 名法國，也都在歐洲。亞洲地區排名最好的是日本的第 8 名，美國製造僅居第 10 名。<br />\n<br />\n排名\t產地\t消費者印象指數\t主要產品<br />\n1\t德國\t100\t汽車<br />\n2\t瑞士\t98\t黃金<br />\n3\t歐盟\t92\tN/A<br />\n4\t英國\t91\t汽車<br />\n5\t瑞典\t90\t汽車<br />\n6\t加拿大\t85\t汽車<br />\n7\t義大利\t84\t醫藥<br />\n8\t日本\t81\t汽車<br />\n9\t法國\t81\t汽車<br />\n10\t美國\t81\t精煉油<br />\n調查內容摘要: <a href=\"https://www.statista.com/page/Made-In-Country-Index\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fpage%2FMade-In-Country-Index&d=Fy44ZujKm9oT4Thc8K%2FcJf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f5437756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statista.com/page/Made-In-Country-Index</a>"},{"pid":"646a9350ff05918c2356f1bda5044c642a44e5c4","tid":472041,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/3948840/l/ca35bdb7c28e24127275c69bf9c098a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F3948840%2Fl%2Fca35bdb7c28e24127275c69bf9c098a1.jpg&h=b2b36a4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eaacf0e4e1aaecc3bc98eabfd50b79afc8bd827","tid":472041,"uid":123969,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:39:01.000Z","msg":"如果係啲標籤到見到made in europe淨係會覺得係啲東歐國家做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b457f7c9a3079b4b1aeead7753077166cadb837","tid":472041,"uid":62424,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:39:59.000Z","msg":"雙11 呢到有幾多人上淘寶買野？"},{"pid":"8fa5255a81585d92cbe25033be2b192f3208fe51","tid":472041,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80f5b82970ebf575a36ade999979d39538dbc9e","tid":472041,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:52:02.000Z","msg":"hk ?"},{"pid":"71b9dc5fdfb52923739351cd2068e9a3e627a3ff","tid":472041,"uid":38523,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雙11 呢到有幾多人上淘寶買野？</blockquote><br />\n得呢度既支狗買<br />\n仲有<br />\n你spin得好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不願面對現實"},{"pid":"c981b22c81d7067abd887dae584a3b25307420f7","tid":472041,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雙11 呢到有幾多人上淘寶買野？</blockquote><br />\n得呢度既支狗買<br />\n仲有<br />\n你spin得好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不願面對現實</blockquote><br />\n抽插下啲暗撐淘寶就咁大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3ff5ca67696e1b3b8b06